  • ????????:
    Serializable

    @Exported
public class InconsistentDebugInfoException
extends RuntimeException
    Thrown to indicate that there is an inconistency in the debug information provided by the target VM. For example, this exception is thrown if there is a type mismatch between a retrieved value's runtime type and its declared type as reported by the target VM.
